flowchart TD
    T[Try primary path]
    D{Error class?}
    R[Retry with backoff]
    C[Circuit open / fail fast]
    F[Fallback or degrade]
    T --> D
    D -->|transient| R
    D -->|saturated| C
    D -->|recoverable| F
    R --> T
